Quote: LING (HOKARARI) <i> Genypterus blacodes </i> (Bloch and Schneider)  [ibid. 340] In some parts of Nelson Province I have heard Ling referred to as Cloudy Bay Cod on account of its `cloudy' appearance and its being not unlike Red Cod. In Australia, this fish is known as Rockling.
